•Grace Mugabe crying as Obasanjo is consoling her HARARE – Zimbabwe’s former First Lady, Grace Mugabe has been caught on camera crying to Nigeria’s former President, Olusegun Obasanjo at the funeral of her husband, Robert Mugabe.Mugabe, who died on 6 September at Gleneagles Hospital, Singapore, led Zimbabwe for more than three decades. His funeral service was held yesterday in Harare, Zimbabwe. 